        "_account_id": 109,
        "name": "Christopher J. Morrone",
        "email": "morrone2@llnl.gov",
        "username": "morrone"
      },
      "date": "2013-10-24 20:11:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nThe only autoconf substitution macros allowed in the lustre.spec.in file are those associated with version numbers.\n\nWe don't want multiple .src.rpm files that look identical to users, but in fact only work on certain systems or behave differently depending on how configure was run before \"make srpm\" time.  We want one canonical source rpm.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "e5a549114956b14412f3df1884d5844bc21581ec",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 2,
